OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man, 20, who
OL,4,Cdied in A1M crash
OL,6,FThe family of a 20-year-old man who
OL,7,Fdied in a crash on the A1M have said
OL,8,Ftheir "hearts are destroyed."
OL,10,FJordan Orrock, from South Shields,
OL,11,Fdied after the car he was driving was
OL,12,Finvolved in a crash near Chester-le-
OL,13,FStreet at around 10.50pm on Sunday 26
OL,14,FApril.
OL,16,FIn a tribute, his family described him
OL,17,Fas "the life and soul of the party who
OL,18,Flit up every room he walked into".
OL,26,@pD@GOUyD@DOU
