OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777551071
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man, 20, who
OL,4,Cdied in A1M crash
OL,6,FThey said: "Jordan will be sadly
OL,7,Fmissed by his mam, Angela, his
OL,8,Fsiblings Ryan, Lewis, Jamie and
OL,9,FCharlie, his right-hand man, his dog
OL,10,FTyson, and his beloved family and
OL,11,Ffriends.
OL,13,F"Our family's hearts are destroyed.
OL,15,F"We would like to thank everyone for
OL,16,Ftheir support during this difficult
OL,17,Ftime, and would ask that we are left
OL,18,Falone to grieve in peace."
OL,26,@nD@LOUuD@AOUwD@AOUzD@ZO]
