OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777551071
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man, 20, who
OL,4,Cdied in A1M crash
OL,6,FPolice say the black Mercedes A-Class
OL,7,FJordan was driving is believed to have
OL,8,Fstruck the central reservation before
OL,9,Fcoming to rest on its roof.
OL,11,FA 20-year-old passenger who was also
OL,12,Fin the car died on Monday night.
OL,14,FA second passenger, also aged 20, was
OL,15,Ftaken to hospital and is being treated
OL,16,Fwith serious injuries.
OL,18,FOfficers are appealing for witnesses
OL,19,For anyone with dashcam footage of the
OL,20,Fvehicle before the collision to come
OL,21,Fforward.
